				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I was practicing with Call of the Arch Mage last night using the Imps in Lavastorm working out all the piffy nuances of charming. Tab-Lock, Mez, Bebuff, yadda yadda yadda.
<br />

<br />
The majority of the time the spell only kept the critter charmed for about 5 minutes.  A very green critter!
<br />

<br />
Is this average for this spell? 
<br />

<br />
I mean it is a lvl 65 spell, it should have more usefulness than 5 minutes and capped at 60. 
<br />

<br />
Any advice beyond what is listed in the Library?<br />_________________<br />Malaprop - Gnome of Action.
<br />
"Initiative comes to thems that wait."</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
