<br />

<br />
The spell has a duration of up to 20 minutes.  That means anywhere from 1 second to 20 mins duration.  There is debate about higher CHA making a difference.  Try raising your charisma with steins and a buff from an enchanter to see if you notice any difference.
<br />

<br />
I am not a big fan of Mage Charming - we summon and control pets 100% throughout the game until we get this spell.  It does have it's limited uses, so it is not a bad spell.
<br />

<br />
Good job testing it out and getting to understand the spell before you use it in a group situation.
<br />

<br />
