			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Charming is basic
<br />

<br />
1. Durations is Random and based of the magic resistance of the mob.  IF you debuff the mob with sina you have a good chance of a decent duration.  IF u notice while in bot charm brakes w/i 1 min of malosinia wearing off.
<br />

<br />
2. Charisma has nothing to do with the duration of charm.  Charisma only helps with the landing the spell.  Higher your charisma less chance of resistance.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=363234" target="_blank" class="postlink"> <img src="http://www.ciguild.com/pics/uploads/tag.jpg" border="0" /> </a>
<br />
Arch Convoker <a href="http://www.ciguild.com" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: blue">Caelum Infinitum</span> </a> <span style="color: green"><span style="font-style: italic">Fennin Ro </span></span>
